Case No. 4,111. DUCATUR v. The DESIRE.

[Bee, 385.]

Admiralty Court of Pennsylvania. 1779. Prize—Recapture. French owners are entitled to the benefit of 1he ordinance of congress relative to recaptures. The question was whether French owners should have the benefit of the ordinance of congress relative to recaptures, and it was so determined. [Before HOPKTNSON, District Judge.]
